    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a species of flying insects that are common in the homes of humans, having a gray thorax, four longitudinal dark lines on the back, yellow underside of the abdomen, and a body covered with hair. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
